Explain the actions taken by the IT department to investigate the incident: immediately a packet analyzer tool was deployed and then checked the condition on site where we came to know that port 53 is unreachable.

Note key findings of the IT department's investigation (i.e., details related to the port affected, DNS server, etc.): The affected port was port 53 and is used for DNS servers.

